Starice/Alpha Dolphy::


"Are your ready to go to Maximal City?" asked Alpha.

"But the baby...?"said Starice while she looked the little Eyebright.

"Don't worry all that she needs is in Shuttle...  "

"Thanks Alpha"

"You're welcome" replied Alpha.

Starice walked to Shuttle with Eyebright in arms, she boarded the 
shuttle and it took off to Maximal City.

Alpha opened comm link with Epyon "Boss bot?  it's Alpha, Starice an 
the baby are on a shuttle and they're going to Maximal city "
